lyrics: Sumanasavandita sundari madhavi chandra sahodari hemamaye
Jayajaya he Madhusudana kamini, Adilakshmi sada palaya mam.
Jayajaya he Madhusudana kamini, Dhanyalakshmi sada palaya mam.
Jayajaya he Madhusudana kamini, Dhairyalakshmi sada palaya mam.
Harihara Brahma supujita sevita, tapanivarini padayute.
Jayajaya he Madhusudana kamini, Gajalakshmi rupena palaya mam.
Ahikhaga vahini mohini chakrini ragavivardhini jnanamaye
Jayajaya he Madhusudana kamini, Santanalakshmi tvam palaya mam.
Kanakadharastuti Vaibhava Vandita, Shankara Desika Manya Pade.
Jayajaya he Madhusudana Kamini, Vijayalakshmi Sada Palaya Mam.
Pranata Sureshwari Bharati Bhargavi Shokavinashini Ratnamaye
Jayajaya he Madhusudana Kamini, Vidyalakshmi Sada Palaya Mam.
Dhimidhimi Dhindhimi Dhindhimi Dhindhimi Dundubhi Nada Supurnamaye
Ghumaghum Ghunghum Ghunghum Ghunghum, Shankhaninada Suvadyanute.
Jayajaya he Madhusudana Kamini, Dhanalakshmi Rupena Palaya Mam.
